sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant FastAPI
    participant Django
    
    User->>Frontend: Enter email/password
    Frontend->>FastAPI: POST /auth/login
    FastAPI->>Django: Query User model
    Django-->>FastAPI: User + role
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Verify password & generate JWT
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: JWT token
    Frontend->>Frontend: Store token in localStorage
    Frontend->>FastAPI: GET /deals (with JWT header)
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Verify JWT & extract user
    FastAPI->>Django: Query Deals (filtered by role)
    Django-->>FastAPI: Deals list
    FastAPI-->>Frontend: Deals JSON